# S04-T06: Ring Buffer

## Objective
Fixed-size ring buffer for telemetry history feeding graphs and replay.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `src/shared/util/RingBuffer.ts` — generic `RingBuffer<T>`.
- Operations: `push`, `at(i)`, `toArray()`, `size`, `capacity`.
- O(1) push/access. Typed-array specialization for `Float32Array` (telemetry numeric series).
- Capacity per series: 600 samples (~60s @ 10Hz).

## Steps
1. Implement generic class.
2. Add `Float32RingBuffer` specialization.
3. Wire per-field buffers in `useTelemetryStore`.
4. Bind to Graph components (S03-T04).

## Invariants
- No allocations on push (overwrite-in-place).
- Order preserved via head/tail indices.
- Read access never reorders contents.
